_:b0__93115 <http://www.w3.org/ns/locn#geometry> "POLYGON((10.79 65.91,24.18 65.91,24.18 55.25,10.79 55.25,10.79 65.91))"^^<http://www.opengis.net/ont/geosparql#wktLiteral>;
