<feed> <https://w3id.org/tree#member> <#945613984c3d0b28ddec1fca22f0265c>.
<#945613984c3d0b28ddec1fca22f0265c> a <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#Create>;
    <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#object> <https://admin.dataportal.se/store/818/resource/bdc91dd235551821aec077ad565c6194>;
