    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/description> "FTIR analysis of samples from a palaeolithic sandstone object from Mühlheim-Dietesheim, Germany. The upload includes raw data, images of analysis points and a report describing the samples, analysis points, method, instrumentation and interpretation. Related to project RAÄ-2024-0156."@en;
