    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/description> "GENERAL INFORMATION- Dataset title: Structural conversion of the spidroin C-terminal domain during assembly of spider silk fibers- Description: The dataset contains raw data associated with the publication with the same name, accepted for publication in Nature Communications.- Authors: Danilo Hirabae De Oliveira, Vasantha Gowda, Tobias Sparrman, Linnea Gustafsson, Rodrigo Sanches Pires, Christian Riekel, Andreas Barth, Christofer Lendel, My Hedhammar \n\nORGANIZATIONThe folder contains zip-files for each figure in the publication. Each zip-file contains data and a .txt file describing the content, the methods for data acquisition and analysis, and the file types.\n\nDATA COLLECTIONData collection and analysis is described in the paper and in the .txt files included in each zip-file."@en;
    a <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#Dataset>
}

