    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/description> "Three datasets (for ATTO Tower, Hyytiälä and Zeppelin stations):\n\nContain hourly Particle Number Size Distributions and air mass history (96 hours) calculated using Hysplit - Hybrid Single Particle Lagrangian Integrated Trajectory model. Precipitation rates along trajectories are collocated using TRMM for the Atto dataset, and other meteorological conditions are given from GDAS1 reanalysis (output from Hysplit)."@en;
