<feed> <https://w3id.org/tree#member> <#50bf9fe647529dd387ccb718d4dd0a78>.
<#50bf9fe647529dd387ccb718d4dd0a78> a <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#Create>;
    <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#object> <https://admin.dataportal.se/store/818/resource/f1fe1c9321f29565a242b2531bcc0a39>;
