<https://admin.dataportal.se/store/818/resource/40bb74397872581c8950aae338d2d25b> <http://purl.org/dc/terms/issued> "2021-03-10T00:00:00Z"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/modified> "2023-12-31T00:00:00Z"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/title> "OPEN-KTH: An Open Lidar Dataset of KTH Campus Valhallavägen"@en;
    <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#theme> <http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/data-theme/TECH>;
    <http://www.w3.org/ns/prov#qualifiedAttribution> _:b0__6900.
_:b0__6900 <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#hadRole> <http://inspire.ec.europa.eu/metadata-codelist/ResponsiblePartyRole/principalInvestigator>;
    <http://www.w3.org/ns/prov#agent> <https://admin.dataportal.se/store/818/resource/b9ae233c2eb630d9ba52c10366ea83b0>;
    a <http://www.w3.org/ns/prov#Attribution>.
<https://admin.dataportal.se/store/818/resource/40bb74397872581c8950aae338d2d25b> <http://www.w3.org/ns/prov#qualifiedAttribution> _:b0__8353.
_:b0__8353 <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#hadRole> <http://inspire.ec.europa.eu/metadata-codelist/ResponsiblePartyRole/principalInvestigator>;
    <http://www.w3.org/ns/prov#agent> <https://admin.dataportal.se/store/818/resource/abc220e4dc01b16e21ae67d600ab6cc7>;
    a <http://www.w3.org/ns/prov#Attribution>.
<https://admin.dataportal.se/store/818/resource/40bb74397872581c8950aae338d2d25b> <http://purl.org/dc/terms/accessRights> <http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/access-right/PUBLIC>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/publisher> <http://dataportal.se/organisation/SE2021003054>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/description> "OPEN-KTH: An open Lidar dataset of KTH campus Valhallavägen\n\nOpen-KTH is a subproject of the AD-EYE testbed for Automated Driving and Intelligent Transportation Systems.\n\nLearn more at https://www.adeye.se/open-kth or contact adeye@md.kth.se\n\nThe AD-EYE testbed is based on the design presented in the work :\n\nNaveen Mohan, Martin Törngren, \"AD-EYE: A Co-Simulation Platform for Early Verification of Functional Safety Concepts\", SAE Technical Paper 19AE-0203/2019-01-0126, https://doi.org/10.4271/2019-01-0126\n\nPreprint available at: https://arxiv.org/abs/1912.00448\n\nData collected by students of the group \"AD-EYE on Road\" in the capstone course of the Mechatronics Masters program using the AD-EYE platform.\n\nMapping using the collected data was performed by Maxime Sainte Catherine from the AD-EYE team.\n\nThe data around \"Försvarshögskolan\", the Swedish Defence Academy, has been intentionally removed. As of 09-09-2021, there is no intention of restoring this missing data due to lack of legal clarity on what is publishable about this building."@en;
    a <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#Dataset>
}

