    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/modified> "2026-03-25T16:37:57.234997"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/title> "Trafikmätning för cykel"@sv, "Traffic measurement for bicycles"@en, "Trafikmåling for cykler"@da;
    <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#theme> <http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/data-theme/TRAN>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/temporal> _:b0__2305.
_:b0__2305 <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#startDate> "1994-01-01"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#date>;
    a <http://purl.org/dc/terms/PeriodOfTime>.
<https://opendata-api.malmo.se/dataset/00b1590e-a504-4c55-a7f2-3d6fd659d982> a <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#Dataset>
