<feed> <https://w3id.org/tree#member> <#259211f1d8bc8fa1ac73f36f8eee50e9>.
<#259211f1d8bc8fa1ac73f36f8eee50e9> a <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#Update>;
    <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#object> <http://api.kolada.se/v3/kpi/N85071>;
