<feed> <https://w3id.org/tree#member> <#3ec2de6fc4e10fd0f788d21eb495f984>.
<#3ec2de6fc4e10fd0f788d21eb495f984> a <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#Update>;
    <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#object> <https://admin.dataportal.se/store/818/resource/925787dfd5709efa2744a77ffcd0520b>;
